OL,3,CRider 'heartbroken' as horse dies
OL,4,Cafter crash with tractor
OL,6,FA horse rider is pleading with drivers
OL,7,Fto be more careful after the horse she
OL,8,Fcalls her 'best friend' had to be put
OL,9,Fdown, following an incident involving
OL,10,Fa tractor.
OL,12,FAmy Hilton says she has been left
OL,13,Fheartbroken after her seven-year-old
OL,14,Fhorse Archie died after a crash on a
OL,15,Fquiet rural lane near Benenden, Kent,
OL,16,Fin February.
