OL,3,CRider 'heartbroken' as horse dies
OL,4,Cafter crash with tractor
OL,6,FMs Hilton says he was hit by a
OL,7,Ftractor's trailer that had been driven
OL,8,Ftoo close and too fast, so she wants
OL,9,Fto honour his memory by educating
OL,10,Fdrivers on how to approach horses on
OL,11,Fthe road.
OL,13,FAmy Hilton said: "I want drivers to
OL,14,Funderstand we're all in it together,
OL,15,Fall sharing the road and we need to
OL,16,Fall respect each other."
OL,18,F"The only option we had was to put him
OL,19,Fdown and that was tough because he was
OL,20,Fonly seven," Ms Hilton added.
