OL,3,CRider 'heartbroken' as horse dies
OL,4,Cafter crash with tractor
OL,6,F"Archie was my horse, and he was my
OL,7,Feverything. Horses aren't just a pet,
OL,8,Fthey're my whole life.
OL,10,F"I've put in everything to that horse
OL,11,Fand he just didn't deserve what
OL,12,Fhappened.
OL,14,FArchie was a thoroughbred cross Irish
OL,15,Fsports horse, worth tens of thousands
OL,16,Fof pounds, and was about to start the
OL,17,Feventing season.
