OL,3,CRider 'heartbroken' as horse dies
OL,4,Cafter crash with tractor
OL,6,FArchie's mother had competed at a high
OL,7,Flevel but died giving birth to him, so
OL,8,FMs Hilton had bottle-fed Archie and
OL,9,Flater spent five years training him.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for Kent Police said:
OL,12,F"At around 1.40pm on Tuesday 18
OL,13,FFebruary 2025 officers on patrol in
OL,14,FIden Green, near Benenden were flagged
OL,15,Fdown following a collision involving a
OL,16,Ftractor and a horse in Standen Street.
OL,18,F"The driver has since been identified
OL,19,Fand police say enquiries into the
OL,20,Fincident are ongoing.
